thread.title: As U.S. students walk out, one gets shot at Florida school

title: As U.S. students walk out, one gets shot at Florida school
text:
As U.S. students walk out, one gets shot at Florida school Friday, April 20, 2018 - 00:30 
Police deployed Friday to the scene of a school shooting near Ocala, Florida where one student was hurt. The shooting happened as students across the country prepared to walkout of their schools to protest gun violence. . Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
